%h2
  Step 1: Request Code

%form{method: 'GET', action: iri.cut('/mobile/send')}
  = Rack::Csrf.tag(env)
  %fieldset
    %label
      Enter your mobile phone in
      %a{href: 'https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/E.164'} E.164
      format (digits only, no leading zeros):
    %input{type: 'text', name: 'phone', placeholder: '12125551122', pattern: '[0-9]+', autocomplete: 'off', required: true, tabindex: 1, autofocus: true}
    %input{type: 'submit', tabindex: 3, value: 'Request'}

%p
  The
  %a{href: 'https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/SMS'} SMS
  will arrive to your mobile phone
  within the next three minutes.

%p
  You can also use your GitHub account to
  = succeed ',' do
    %a{href: login_link} login
  but only if you work in
  = succeed '.' do
    %a{href: 'https://www.0crat.com/team'} Zerocracy

%p
  = succeed ':' do
    %strong.firebrick ATTENTION
  By logging in you automatically accept the
  = succeed '.' do
    %a{href: iri.cut('/terms')} Terms of Use
